00:30:14,422 --> 00:30:19,064
So the question was, what is the impact on revenue of sales?

509
00:30:19,464 --> 00:30:21,786
And I think there are two types of sales, and it's very

510
00:30:21,846 --> 00:30:24,307
important to think about them differently.

511
00:30:24,947 --> 00:30:26,988
One is a sale where you're selling currency.

